{"tid":681951,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"幫懶醒既人砌機真係慘過食屎","createTime":"2018-05-28T12:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T08:41:28.000Z","uid":142854,"like":494,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"bdae93cf78ab1ae6634be021461b6aeb4cb3b6ba","tid":681951,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"1.咩都唔識 但係要嘈用咩件<br />\n2600x + B250m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同我講i5 8400 &gt; R5 2600 我問點得返黎<br />\n佢俾張i5 2400 vs i5 8400 圖我...<br />\n<br />\n2. 度縮<br />\n唔識砌就成套買哂佢啦 買手機捨得用七八千 電腦反而想平D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時問廠機留低既500gb hdd可唔可以加埋落去(list有3TB) 仲有火牛機箱 乜乜乜<br />\n一時問可唔可以唔買mon 屋企有 <br />\n講左有機會舊mon冇DVI用唔到check清楚<br />\n最後冇買mon 送到黎真係用唔到舊mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (正正係因為冇dvi頭,張卡又冇VGA)<br />\n又要加錢落屋村電腦鋪用水魚價買Mon<br />\n<br />\nwindows用咩呢D唔洗講<br />\n佢用隻古董usb燒<br />\n都講到明遲D有機會再用 用幾十買隻好D<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都要慳</span> 燒左半日<br />\n最後裝左唔知幾耐 問我乜windows裝咁慢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.自作聰明<br />\n拆完屋企舊機再砌返當識砌<br />\n想慳砌機費<br />\n送到黎只係識放粒cpu同未插實既ram<br />\n要我上去幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 懷疑多多<br />\n俾list佢<br />\n係咁問點解人地電腦鋪又係 r5/i7  會平D(幾十)<br />\n都係8gb ram咋嘛<br />\n我心諗 金牛變機箱送既GTR牛 3000 ram變2400 ram 連SSD都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解舊件唔用得果D真係廢事答<br />\nddr2 ram ide hdd 300W牛等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係6年中學同學真係直接block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"698eeb373dbff1234ed5106138135b617d2cf5f0","tid":681951,"uid":14766,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"你咪叫佢